Invocation Name: word jumble
des: Play an interesting game of quiz with Alexa. While playing the quiz, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next question. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the quiz. have fun answering questions with jumbled words for you to decipher :)
